    variables_required:
    - feature_name
    - odoo_version
    template: '## Understanding {feature_name} in Odoo {odoo_version}


      {feature_name} configuration directly impacts online revenue generation, customer
      shopping experience, and conversion rates. Unlike back-office configurations,
      {feature_name} changes immediately affect how customers interact with your digital
      storefront—misconfigured settings create abandoned carts, payment failures,
      and lost sales opportunities.


      {feature_specific_intro}


      ## {feature_name} Configuration Workflow


      {feature_setup_workflow}


      ### Prerequisites and Module Dependencies


      {feature_name} requires specific Odoo modules installed before accessing configuration
      screens:


      {prerequisite_configuration}


      Navigate to Apps, search for required modules, and click Install. Verify all
      prerequisite modules show "Installed" status before proceeding.


      ## Core Configuration Settings


      {core_settings_section}


      ### Business Rules and Automation


      {computation_rules}


      ### Performance Optimization


      {performance_optimization}


      ## Common Configuration Mistakes


      {common_mistakes}


      ### Testing and Validation Checklist


      Before declaring {feature_name} configuration complete, validate these scenarios:


      {validation_checklist}

      '
    variable_mappings:
      feature_specific_intro:
        Product Variants: Product variant configuration enables offering multiple
          versions of products without creating separate records for each combination.
          Misconfigured variants create inventory nightmares and customer confusion.
        Shipping Methods: Shipping method configuration determines delivery options
          and cost calculations at checkout. Misconfigured shipping blocks orders
          or creates unexpected costs.
        Coupon Codes: Coupon code configuration controls promotional discounts and
          usage restrictions. Misconfigured coupons create revenue leakage or customer
          frustration.
        Abandoned Cart: Abandoned cart recovery automates email campaigns for incomplete
          checkouts. Poor configuration sends too many or too few recovery emails.
        default: This configuration feature plays a critical role in Odoo's operational
          functionality. Proper configuration ensures seamless integration with your
          business processes and delivers expected outcomes. Misconfiguration creates
          operational friction that compounds into permanent inefficiencies, forcing
          users to develop workarounds that persist even after the underlying issue
          is fixed. Configuration decisions made here affect all users and transactions
          across the system.
      feature_setup_workflow:
        Product Variants: 1. Navigate to Sales > Products > Variants\n2. Define product
          attributes\n3. Configure variant generation rules\n4. Set variant-specific
          pricing\n5. Configure inventory tracking per variant\n6. Test variant display
          and selection
        Shipping Methods: 1. Navigate to Website > Configuration > Shipping\n2. Create
          delivery carriers\n3. Configure pricing rules\n4. Set availability conditions\n5.
          Enable carrier integrations\n6. Test checkout shipping display
        Coupon Codes: 1. Navigate to Website > Configuration > Promo Codes\n2. Define
          discount mechanics\n3. Set usage restrictions\n4. Configure validity periods\n5.
          Generate coupon codes\n6. Test coupon application
        Abandoned Cart: 1. Navigate to Website > Configuration > Cart Recovery\n2.
          Define abandonment criteria\n3. Create email templates\n4. Configure send
          schedule\n5. Set exclusion rules\n6. Monitor recovery metrics
        default: '1. **Access Configuration**: Navigate to the appropriate Configuration
          menu within the relevant module

          2. **Review Prerequisites**: Verify required modules are installed and company
          settings configured

          3. **Configure Core Settings**: Define key parameters and default values

          4. **Set User Permissions**: Assign appropriate access rights to user groups

          5. **Test Configuration**: Create test records to verify behavior matches
          requirements

          6. **Document Changes**: Record configuration decisions and expected impacts

          7. **Deploy to Production**: Apply validated settings to live environment'
      prerequisite_configuration:
        Product Variants: Install Website module for e-commerce, Sales module for
          orders, and Inventory module for stock tracking. Configure product attributes
          before creating variants.
        Shipping Methods: Install Website and Delivery modules. Establish carrier
          accounts before configuring API integrations.
        Coupon Codes: Install Website and Sales modules. Marketing Automation module
          optional for advanced campaigns.
        Abandoned Cart: Install Website module with email marketing capabilities enabled.
        default: '- **Required modules**: Core Odoo modules must be installed before
          configuring this feature

          - **User permissions**: Appropriate access rights for configuration and
          usage

          - **Company settings**: Basic company configuration completed including
          fiscal year and currency

          - **Database backup**: Recent backup before making configuration changes

          - **Test environment**: Development instance available for testing before
          production deployment'
      core_settings_section:
        Product Variants: Configure variant display mode, inventory management level,
          pricing strategy, and image association in Sales > Products > Variants settings.
        Shipping Methods: Set delivery carrier setup, cost calculation method, geographic
          restrictions, and free shipping thresholds in Website > Shipping configuration.
        Coupon Codes: Define discount type, code generation, usage limits, validity
          period, and product restrictions in promo code settings.
        Abandoned Cart: Set abandonment time threshold, email template design, send
          schedule, and exclusion rules in cart recovery configuration.
        default: Configuration options are accessible through the module's Configuration
          menu. Key settings include enabling/disabling feature flags, defining default
          values, establishing validation rules, and customizing behavior to match
          your business requirements. Configuration changes typically apply at company
          level unless explicitly scoped to user groups or specific records. Review
          each setting carefully as changes affect system-wide behavior.
      computation_rules:
        Product Variants: 'Odoo calculates variant pricing using: variant-specific
          price > base price + attribute surcharges > pricelist rules > customer pricing.'
        Shipping Methods: 'Shipping costs calculated by: free shipping check > base
          method calculation > promotional discounts > final cart total.'
        Coupon Codes: 'Discount application order: product promotions > coupon discounts
          > customer pricelists. Validate code before applying.'
        Abandoned Cart: System identifies abandoned carts after configured time threshold
          and triggers email sequence based on schedule.
        default: Configuration follows standard Odoo patterns with settings organized
          hierarchically. Company-level settings establish system-wide defaults that
          apply to all users and transactions. User group permissions control access
          to configuration screens and feature usage. Transaction-level settings override
          company defaults when specific behavior is required for individual records.
      performance_optimization:
        Product Variants: Index variant attribute fields for fast filtering. Lazy
          load variant images. Monitor query time on category pages with many variants.
        Shipping Methods: Cache shipping rate calculations. Set reasonable cache expiration
          balancing freshness vs performance.
        Coupon Codes: Test checkout performance with complex discount rules. Immediate
          calculation provides confidence but adds processing time.
        Abandoned Cart: Schedule cart recovery emails during off-peak hours to avoid
          system load during high traffic periods.
        default: Optimize performance by configuring appropriate database indexes,
          limiting automated action frequency, and archiving old records that no longer
          require active processing. Monitor system performance after configuration
          changes to identify bottlenecks. Large-scale deployments may require infrastructure
          scaling.
      common_mistakes:
        Product Variants: Avoid generating all possible attribute combinations automatically.
          Create variants manually for actual product offerings only.
        Shipping Methods: Validate actual shipping costs before setting flat rates.
          Configure weight-based overrides for heavy items.
        Coupon Codes: Configure coupon mutual exclusivity to prevent stacking that
          destroys margins. Set both validity date AND usage limit.
        Abandoned Cart: Balance email frequency - neither too annoying nor missing
          recovery window. Exclude already-purchased carts.
        default: Common configuration errors include enabling features without prerequisite
          modules, configuring in wrong order (company settings before user permissions),
          skipping testing phase with non-production data, and failing to document
          configuration decisions for future reference. These mistakes create issues
          that are difficult to diagnose and require time-consuming rollback procedures.
      validation_checklist:
        Product Variants: Test variant selection UI on mobile. Verify inventory decrements
          at variant level. Confirm variant images update correctly.
