          leave balance calculations. Enable calendar integration. Set up conflict
          detection for overlapping requests. Configure leave allocation automation.
        Performance Appraisal: Navigate to Appraisals > Configuration. Define review
          cycle periods. Configure evaluation forms and criteria. Set up goal setting
          workflows. Enable 360-degree feedback collection. Configure rating scales.
          Define competency frameworks. Set up performance improvement plans. Enable
          appraisal calibration sessions.
        Payroll Configuration: Navigate to Payroll > Configuration. Define salary
          structures by employee category. Configure tax jurisdiction mapping. Set
          up benefit deduction rules. Enable direct deposit configuration. Configure
          payroll calendars. Define earning and deduction codes. Set up payroll register
          generation. Configure statutory compliance reporting.
        default: '1. Review business requirements for this feature

          2. Enable required modules and dependencies

          3. Configure company-level defaults

          4. Set up user access permissions

          5. Test with sample transactions

          6. Document configuration and train users

          7. Deploy to production environment'
      prerequisite_configuration:
        Project Timesheet: Install Project module for task tracking. Install Timesheet
          module for time entry. Install Sales module for billing integration. Install
          Accounting module for revenue recognition. Configure user access rights
          before enabling timesheet tracking.
        Project Billing: Install Project module. Install Sales module for quotations
