      permission_requirements:
        Project Timesheet: employees need timesheet user rights to submit hours, project
          managers require timesheet approval rights, finance team needs billing conversion
          access, and system administrators control timesheet configuration settings
        Project Billing: project managers need billing configuration access, finance
          team requires invoice generation rights, sales team needs contract setup
