        Project Timesheet: Automated actions populate tasks from sales orders, send
          timesheet submission reminders, lock timesheets after approval deadline,
          generate draft invoices from approved timesheets, and alert managers of
          missing timesheet entries.
        Project Billing: Automation creates invoices from approved timesheets and
          expenses, applies prepaid service deductions, generates milestone-based
          invoices on completion, sends billing notifications to customers, and creates
          revenue recognition journal entries.
        Expense Management: Automation extracts data from receipt images, categorizes
