          GPS data, converts foreign currency expenses, and sends expense report submission
          reminders.
        Leave Management: Automated workflows calculate leave accruals each pay period,
          send leave balance notifications, route approval requests to managers, update
          team calendars on approval, and trigger payroll adjustments for unpaid leave.
