        default: Automated actions execute based on record triggers, field value changes,
          or scheduled timing. Configure automation carefully to prevent infinite
          loops, ensure idempotent operations, and handle error conditions gracefully.
      integration_modules:
        Project Timesheet: Sales (service contracts), Accounting (revenue recognition),
          Invoicing (billing generation), HR (employee rates), and Projects (task
          tracking)
        Project Billing: Sales (quotations and orders), Timesheets (billable hours),
          Expenses (billable costs), Accounting (invoice posting), and Subscriptions
