        Leave Management: Request leave, verify approval routing, test balance calculations,
          confirm calendar integration, validate carryover rules, and verify payroll
          integration for unpaid leave
        Performance Appraisal: Launch test review cycle, complete self-assessment,
          submit manager evaluation, verify scoring calculation, test goal tracking,
