    variable_mappings:
      localization_introduction:
        Localization Usa: 'Odoo''s US localization module provides comprehensive support
          for federal and state-level tax compliance, including sales tax nexus management,
          1099 reporting, and state-specific tax rate configuration. The module integrates
          with major US accounting standards (US GAAP) and supports multi-state operations
          with automatic tax jurisdiction determination based on shipping addresses.

          '
        Localization Uk: 'Odoo''s UK localization enables full compliance with HMRC''s
          Making Tax Digital (MTD) requirements, supporting both quarterly VAT returns
          and annual corporation tax filings. The module includes pre-configured charts
          of accounts following FRS 102 and IFRS standards, Construction Industry
          Scheme (CIS) deduction management, and automated VAT submission through
          the HMRC API.

          '
        Localization Germany: 'Germany''s localization module ensures GoBD (Grundsätze
          zur ordnungsmäßigen Führung und Aufbewahrung von Büchern) compliance with
          tamper-proof accounting records and audit trail functionality. The module
          supports DATEV export for tax advisor collaboration, Elster VAT return submission,
          SKR03/SKR04 chart of accounts templates, and cash-basis accounting requirements
          for small businesses.

          '
        Localization India Gst: 'India''s GST localization handles the complex multi-tier
          tax structure with CGST (Central GST), SGST (State GST), IGST (Integrated
          GST), and Cess calculations based on supply location and HSN/SAC codes.
          The module supports e-invoicing mandate for businesses above INR 5 crore
          turnover, GSTR-1/2A/3B return filing, TDS/TCS compliance, and integration
          with GST Network (GSTN) through API or third-party GSP.

          '
        Localization France: 'French localization provides FEC (Fichier des Écritures
          Comptables) export functionality required for tax audits, pre-configured
          Plan Comptable Général (PCG) with standard account numbering, automated
          declaration of TVA (VAT) returns, and support for fiscal year alignment
          with calendar year. The module ensures compliance with French accounting
          regulations including mandatory sequential invoice numbering without gaps.

          '
        Localization Australia: 'Australian localization implements GST (Goods and
          Services Tax) with BAS (Business Activity Statement) reporting capabilities,
          supports ATO (Australian Taxation Office) integration for real-time tax
          lodgement, includes Single Touch Payroll (STP) Phase 2 functionality for
          payroll reporting, and provides PAYG withholding calculation for employee
          and contractor payments.

          '
        Localization Canada: 'Canadian localization manages federal GST and provincial
          sales taxes (PST, QST, HST) with automatic rate determination based on province,
          supports bilingual invoicing (English/French) required in Quebec, includes
          T4/T4A slip generation for payroll reporting, and provides CRA (Canada Revenue
